  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_2' aria-label=\" State of Punjab & Ors. versus M/s Om Prakash Brick Kiln Owner, Etc. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('2','2025','2025_1_859_868','2025INSC88'); ><font size='4'> <strong>STATE OF PUNJAB & ORS.<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>M/S OM PRAKASH BRICK KILN OWNER, ETC. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 1 S.C.R. 859</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 88</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010002412025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : ABHAY S. OKA<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, UJJAL BHUYAN</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether the State is entitled to levy royalty on brick earth excavation, irrespective of the issue of ownership of the excavated land. Headnotes&dagger; Power of State Government to levy on royalty on excavation of brick earth &ndash; Punjab Minor Mineral Concession 54A, 54B and 54C of the Punjab Minor Mineral Concession Rules, 1964, the State Government is empowered to levy royalty on the production and disposal of minor minerals &ndash; In the present case, brick earth was declared as a minor mineral, and thus, the State Government was entitled to levy<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 21-01-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 10687/2013</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_1_859_868','2025INSC88','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_1_859_868','2025INSC88','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('2','2025','2025_1_859_868','2025INSC88');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('2','2025','2025_1_859_868','2025INSC88','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
